  "title": "Creative Designer (Retail)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Conceptualize and develop creative ideas for retail environments, events, and brand activations.</li>\n  <li>Design layouts, renders, mockups, and final artwork across digital and print platforms.</li>\n  <li>Specialize in retail solutions, including in-store branding, visual merchandising, and space planning.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with internal teams and external vendors to ensure seamless project execution.</li>\n  <li>Research, adapt, and apply the latest retail and design trends to projects.</li>\n  <li>Prepare accurate production-ready files and liaise with printers and fabricators.</li>\n  <li>Manage multiple projects simultaneously while maintaining brand consistency and high-quality standards.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
